{"tid":1224472,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"『暫你老母』咁我可唔可以暫緩強姦你啊林鄭","createTime":"2019-06-15T03:33:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T03:40:15.000Z","uid":60583,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6784a994bf40bf1ba47b790eae69fcb94acd09d3","tid":1224472,"uid":60583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:33:16.000Z","msg":"咁我可唔可以暫緩強姦你啊林鄭<br />\n<br />\n事實係我連掂都唔想掂你啊屌<br />\n<br />\n就正如我地係一啲都唔想修例<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而唔係要暫緩啊屌！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n『不撤回，不撤退』<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">利申無意強姦任何人，強姦喪盡天良，如同修例</span></span>"},{"pid":"96ccc75af37af8eaec4cd7e49c069a5f222003fe","tid":1224472,"uid":60583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:40:15.000Z","msg":"用強姦比喻有啲過火，我道歉（免得比位人入）<br />\n<br />\n但真係好撚火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}